  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Collection of characteristics of slow coronary flow from approximately 90 patient records</measure>
    <time_frame>Six months</time_frame>
    <description>Characteristics of slow coronary flow will be collected from approximately 90 patient medical records and will analyzed to find the common variables. This analysis will show whether there is any statistical significance to these characteristics.</description>
