    <sampling_method>Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  anginal pain

          -  laboratory markers

          -  pathological ECG for ischemia

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  obstructed coronary artery during catheterization

